title: President congratulates Pakistan cricket team over win against Namibia
content:
In a a tweet on social media platform Twitter, he said, “another good performance by Team Pakistan. Great battingRizwan, Babar Azam and Hafeez. My dear Green Shirts you have the talent & skills, but it is finally in the mind that winning becomes a habit. You continue to make us proud.”
